{"tid":809291,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"以色列最新研究：益力多益生菌無效","createTime":"2018-09-07T05:06:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-08T12:08:34.000Z","uid":165773,"like":26,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"8c598d02897bd05a23b043eac9c89509bcc4308e","tid":809291,"uid":165773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T05:06:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.dmarge.com/2018/09/probiotics.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dmarge.com%2F2018%2F09%2Fprobiotics.html&d=GWE3d9Tn9k6wFOfB12cPS4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=cc357f42\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.dmarge.com/2018/09/probiotics.html</a><br />\n<br />\n@Weizmann Institute of Science<br />\n以色列免疫學家Eran Elinav 發現<br />\n科學界一直以化驗排泄物<br />\n來identify腸道細菌 原來極不準確<br />\n<br />\n1.佢哋今次直接在腸道抽樣<br />\n發現腸道細菌成份組合<br />\n唔單止同排泄物有既唔同<br />\n<br />\n2.而飲用益生菌補充劑既人<br />\n只有好少部分人既腸道<br />\n會保留所飲用既益生菌<br />\n<br />\n3.另外發現 其實並無所謂<br />\n人人都有益既益生菌formula<br />\n因為每個人既腸道所合適細菌組合<br />\n都獨一無二 唔可以一個組合適用全部人<br />\n<br />\n所以有效補充腸道益生菌既方法<br />\n必須為每一個飲用補充劑既人<br />\n度身訂造 市面上補充劑根本無效<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cell.com/cell/fulltext/S0092-8674(18\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cell.com%2Fcell%2Ffulltext%2FS0092-8674%2818&d=GWE3d9Tn9k6wFOfB12cPS4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=5497d922\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cell.com/cell/fulltext/S0092-8674(18</a>)31102-4?_returnURL=https%3A%2F%<a href=\"http://2Flinkinghub.elsevier.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F2Flinkinghub.elsevier.com&d=GWE3d9Tn9k6wFOfB12cPS4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=9cb10c78\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">2Flinkinghub.elsevier.com</a>%2Fretrieve%2Fpii%2FS0092867418311024%3Fshowall%3Dtrue"},{"pid":"9dcf087f92ffa7f571413765443ad30ec42f0441","tid":809291,"uid":6111,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T05:08:07.000Z","msg":"不嬲都只當佢汽水咁飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgm